Welcome to odin-flight-booker.com, <%= @passenger.name %>
============================================================

You have successfully booked your flight!
Here are your flight details:

Flight ID: <%= @booking.flight.id %>
From: <%= @booking.flight.departure_airport.code %>
To: <%= @booking.flight.arrival_airport.code %>
Date: <%= @booking.flight.start_date.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>
Time: <%= @booking.flight.start_time.strftime("%I:%M %p") %>
Duration: <%= @booking.flight.flight_duration %> minutes
Passengers: <%= @booking.passengers.count %>

Passenger Info:
    <% @booking.passengers.each_with_index do |passenger, i| %>
        Passenger <%= i + 1 %>:
        Name: <%= passenger.name %> - Email: <%= passenger.email %>
    <% end %>

To view your booking online, just follow this link: 
<%= @url %>.

Thanks for booking your flight with us and have a great day!
